metadata.title: Flash Mints (Chi Modu - The Second Drop) #1
metadata.description: Introducing Chi Modu's 2nd complete NFT collection: Composed of 1,003 unique NFT editions of Chi Modu's photographs (Each NFT is numbered with a serial number proving its authenticity). This collection represents a portion of Chi Modu’s private collection of photos that he’s shot from over the years. Each NFT tells a story from Chi Modu's perspective about the shot and unlocks exclusive benefits, rewards, and surprises for all NFT holders of this collection.
